text.section:
To qualify for a plot in a State veterans' cemetery:
the applicant must be a veteran who meets the requirements for burial at a national veterans' cemetery or an eligible spouse or dependent of a veteran who meets the requirements of this subsection; and
if a veteran, the veteran must also have been a resident of the State:
when the veteran entered the armed forces;
when the veteran died; or
for 2 years, unless, for a reason that the Department finds compelling, the Department waives the time period.
